data.description: Welcome to a beautiful and spacious home featuring upgrades that add the character and charm you've been looking for and located just minutes away from the newly renovated Pinehurst Country Club's Golf Course No. 8! $2,500 PREFERRED LENDER CREDITStep into the open floor plan and experience the feeling of home with ample natural light and a cozy fireplace perfect for entertaining and family gatherings! The first floor offers a large owner's suite and is a retreat of its own, featuring a spa-like bathroom and large walk-in closet.  A formal dining room, laundry room, half bath and well-appointed kitchen with easy access to the large screened in porch round out the first floor. Upstairs leads to 3 additional bedrooms, two full baths, a study nook, and a large bonus room, additionally there is attic space for all your storage needs!The backyard is expansive and offers a huge deck perfect for any outdoor entertaining with plenty of space to create your own oasis! The three-car garage is ideal for storage, home gym, or a workshop!This stunning home on a half-acre lot in the lovely Juniper Ridge neighborhood is a true masterpiece, offering comfort, style, and ideal access to the Village of Pinehurst or an easy commute to Fort Liberty, Cary, or Raleigh!
